s://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/versions/26-1-2.png\" width=\"5%\" alt=\"26.1.2\">\n<img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/labels/versions/26-2.png\" width=\"5%\" alt=\"26.2\">\n</center>\n\n### Colorful Paradise\n\nBring a whole new level of creativity to Minecraft with 770+ new dye colors! Mod expands the vanilla coloring system with hundreds of additional dyes and makes them useful everywhere you'd expect. Nearly every vanilla colorable block and item can now be customized with these new shades, giving you far more freedom when building and decorating. Whether you're building cozy cottages, futuristic cities, or pixel art masterpieces, Colorful Paradise gives you the palette to bring your imagination to life.\n\n### What does this mod add?\n\n- 770+ unique dye colors\n- Custom Dye Mixing Table for creating new colors\n- Color carpets, candles, glass, terracotta, concrete, and many other vanilla blocks\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/showcase.png\" alt=\"Showcase\">\n\nNothing to show yet :(\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/faq.png\" alt=\"FAQ\">\n\n| Question                             | Answer                                                                               |\n| ------------------------------------ |:------------------------------------------------------------------------------------:|\n| Can I use this mod in my modpack?    | Of course! We do not restrict anyone from using our projects :D                      |\n| Will you port mod to version X?      | We port our mods only to newer versions from version that is now mainly supported (_**26.1+**_)|\n| When the mod gets new update?        | Once I will finish with it, I cannot say the exact date when it will happen.         |\n| Where can I report bugs or suggest my idea? | In our discord server, you can find it in links section.                      |\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/our_projects.png\" alt=\"Our Projects\">\n\n<center>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/colorful-paradise\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/icons/colorful_paradise.png\" width=\"25%\" alt=\"Colorful Paradise\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/motlin\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/icons/motlin.png\" width=\"25%\" alt=\"Motlin\">\n</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ileafcore\" style=\"float: right;\">\n  <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/icons/ileafcore.png\" width=\"25%\" alt=\"IleafCore\">\n</a>\n</center>\n\n# <img src=\"https://ilyuxadwa.github.io/Pages-Design-Assets/minecraft/paragraphs/credits.png\" alt=\"Credits\">\n\n**Developed by the IleafMC Team which is a part of IleafDevelopment.** <a href=\"https://discord.gg/AHPcRheFX9\" style=\"float: right;\">Stay in touch</a>\n\n**All rights reserved by IleafDevelopment.**",
